声sheng1sound/voice/(a measure word, used for sounds)/tone/noise1411WK_L5195
  • 个 個 [ge4] individual/this/that/size/classifier for people or objects in general
  • 声音 聲音 [sheng1 yin1] voice/sound/CL:個|个[ge4]
  • 声 聲 [sheng1] sound/voice/tone/noise/classifier for sounds
  • 声明 聲明 [sheng1 ming2] to state/to declare/statement/declaration/CL:項|项[xiang4],份[fen4]
  • 大声 大聲 [da4 sheng1] loud voice/in a loud voice/loudly
  • 声称 聲稱 [sheng1 cheng1] to claim/to state/to proclaim/to assert
  • 和声 和聲 [he2 sheng1] harmony (music)
  • 声说 聲說 [sheng1 shuo1] to narrate
  • 中声 中聲 [zhong1 sheng1] medial (i.e. middle vowel of a syllable in Asian phonetics)
  • 上声 上聲 [shang3 sheng1] falling and rising tone/third tone in modern Mandarin

  • 请大声一点。 [Qǐng dàshēng yīdiǎn.] A little louder, please.
  • 他大声回答了老师的问题。 [Tā dàshēng huídá le lǎoshī de wèntí.] He loudly answered the teacher's question.
  • 他说得很大声。 [tā shuō de hěn dàshēng. (shou le should also say what was said)] He spoke very loudly.
  • 我也喜欢那个歌手的声音。 [wǒ yě xǐhuān nà ge gēshǒu de shēngyīn .] I like that singer's voice, too.
  • 老师声明明天不能迟到。 [Lǎoshī shēngmíng míngtiān bù néng chídào.] The teacher announced that no one can be late tomorrow.
  • 政府当局发表了一个声明。 [Zhèngfǔ dāngjú fābiǎo le yīge shēngmíng.] The government authorities put out an announcement.
  • 发声不容易。 [Fāshēng bù róngyì.] It's not easy to pronounce the tones.
  • 他睡着的时候，打呼声很响。 [tā shuìzháo de shíhou , dǎhū shēng hěn xiǎng .] He was snoring loudly while he slept.
  • 他高兴得大声呐喊。 [Tā gāoxìng de dàshēng nàhǎn.] He is so happy that he shouted out loud.
  • 政府发表严正声明。 [Zhèngfǔ fābiǎo yánzhèng shēngmíng.] The government put out a stern declaration.
